quotes.quote: The healthy and strong individual is the one who asks for help when he needs it. Whether he's got an abscess on his knee or in his soul
quotes.author: Rona Barrett

quotes.quote: Asking for help does not mean that we are weak or incompetent. It usually indicates an advanced level of honesty and intelligence
quotes.author: Anne Wilson Schaef

quotes.quote: You miss 100% of the shots you don't take
quotes.author: Wayne Gretzky
